{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "1d9b08d9",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Multi-modality pipeline: analyzing single-cell multiome data (ATAC + Gene Expression)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f8766905",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Introduction\n",
    "\n",
    "In this tutorial we will analyze single-cell multiome data data from Peripheral blood mononuclear cells (PBMCs). The dataset used in this tutorial can be found here: http://renlab.sdsc.edu/kai/10x-Multiome/.\n",
    "\n",
    "In addition to SnapATAC2, we will utilize [scanpy](https://scanpy.readthedocs.io/en/stable/) to preprocess the scRNA-seq data."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "74bf734c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import snapatac2 as snap\n",
    "import scanpy as sc"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "575fd61b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Analyze gene expression data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "e664e92a",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "AnnData object with n_obs × n_vars = 9631 × 29095\n",
       "    obs: 'domain', 'cell_type'\n",
       "    var: 'gene_ids', 'feature_types'"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 2,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "rna = snap.read(snap.datasets.pbmc10k_multiome(modality='RNA'), backed=None)\n",
    "rna"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "292daa52-c743-48e9-b28a-4f45a17a8980",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "sc.pp.highly_variable_genes(rna, flavor='seurat_v3', n_top_genes=3000)\n",
    "rna = rna[:, rna.var.highly_variable]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "51efbd3a-8d5d-4d99-9405-464c52598af8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "/projects/ps-renlab2/kai/software/micromamba/lib/python3.9/site-packages/scanpy/preprocessing/_normalization.py:170: UserWarning: Received a view of an AnnData. Making a copy.\n",
      "  view_to_actual(adata)\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "sc.pp.normalize_total(rna, target_sum=1e4)\n",
    "sc.pp.log1p(rna)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "dc51b2d4-91d3-4739-a227-0a49f8b3addc",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "snap.tl.spectral(rna, features=None)\n",
    "snap.tl.umap(rna)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "70b43873-7b7c-41af-b38a-79767804c8ff",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<IPython.core.display.Image object>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 6,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "snap.pl.umap(rna, color='cell_type', interactive=False, height=550)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5fb5b60f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Analyze chromatin accessibility data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "20543636",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "AnnData object with n_obs × n_vars = 9631 × 107194\n",
       "    obs: 'domain', 'cell_type'\n",
       "    var: 'feature_types'\n",
       "    uns: 'spectral_eigenvalue'\n",
       "    obsm: 'X_spectral', 'X_umap'"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 7,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "atac = snap.read(snap.datasets.pbmc10k_multiome(modality='ATAC'), backed=None)\n",
    "atac"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "4fba7468",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "snap.tl.spectral(atac, features=None)\n",
    "snap.tl.umap(atac)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "91253c1f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<IPython.core.display.Image object>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 9,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "snap.pl.umap(atac, color=\"cell_type\", interactive=False, height=550)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "1d4fd460",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Perform joint embedding"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "id": "989b9b85-36fb-491c-8a5c-265866ab688b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "assert (rna.obs_names == atac.obs_names).all()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "id": "8d1cda81-0c6d-4c06-8be6-a24ca818766e",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "2023-04-13 23:04:40 - INFO - Compute normalized views...\n",
      "2023-04-13 23:05:44 - INFO - Compute embedding...\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "embedding = snap.tl.multi_spectral([rna, atac], features=None)[1]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "id": "8186812d-e4ed-4313-bb06-5a45cf5281fb",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "atac.obsm['X_joint'] = embedding\n",
    "snap.tl.umap(atac, use_rep='X_joint')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 15,
   "id": "78271b55-f193-44c3-b931-2bae427e1c53",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<IPython.core.display.Image object>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 15,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "snap.pl.umap(atac, color=\"cell_type\", interactive=False, height=550)"
   ]
  }
 ],
